{"tid":928315,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［理性討論］向井敏明與野田毅到底有無百人斬","createTime":"2018-12-04T17:53:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T02:12:44.000Z","uid":95397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5e4afca1a851e43478a2fded0eca78fcc69e60ed","tid":928315,"uid":95397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T17:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktynffJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktynffJ.png&h=61174a77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n向井敏明遺書：<br />\n我向天地神明發誓完全沒有殺害過俘虜和平民。我絕對不接受南京虐殺事件等罪的罪名。我視死為天命，將日本男兒堂堂之軀化為中國之土。但我的靈魂將回歸大八州島（日本國的古稱）。<br />\n如果以我之死，可以消除中國抗戰八年之痛苦經歷的仇恨，可以成為日華親善、東洋和平之因緣，把我像棄石一樣丟棄，我也感到榮幸。<br />\n<br />\n為中國的奮鬥而祈禱！<br />\n為日本的奮起而祈禱！<br />\n中國萬歲！<br />\n日本萬歲！<br />\n天皇陛下萬歲！<br />\n死後變作護國之鬼！<br />\n向井敏明 十二月三十一日 十時"},{"pid":"a51b823ee33f234ee7d26d4f5603aa2264d2e7c6","tid":928315,"uid":95397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T17:54:52.000Z","msg":"Wiki話日本軍刀斬完人會卷刀，所以連斬唔到咁多個"},{"pid":"a7d8b3d1e7fbfadf001bdee5077f105cf720070d","tid":928315,"uid":95397,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T17:55:42.000Z","msg":"如果佢地真係無斬過<br />\n咁佢地咪係俾內容農場害死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3c4003f3f68f07b7e61d62a6f070138221f55e","tid":928315,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T17:57:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 早排先 google 完，今日連登 po 就有"},{"pid":"a4a15fa894141c959ed1508ea391e42c83ec4316","tid":928315,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a51b823ee33f234ee7d26d4f5603aa2264d2e7c6","tid":928315,"uid":95397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T17:54:52.000Z","msg":"Wiki話日本軍刀斬完人會卷刀，所以連斬唔到咁多個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T18:49:49.000Z","msg":"唔可以拎過第2把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm